22/03/baldurs-gate-3-hub-refresh-image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/baldurs-gate-3-hub-refresh-image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/baldurs-gate-3-hub-refresh-image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>《博德之门 3》</em></a>可能是迄今为止同类游戏中最有趣的游戏之一。得益于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brand/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a>数十年的专业知识， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dungeons-and-dragons"><em>《龙与地下城》</em></a>的游戏体验更加生动，许多玩家对这款游戏的潜力感到兴奋。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-pc-games-3034063">2023 年您需要玩的 8 款最佳 PC 游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>在三年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-iii-early-access-classes-and-everything-you-need-to-know-2658339">抢先体验</a>期间，比利时开发商仔细聆听，创造了一款游戏，它满足了<em>龙与地下城</em>粉丝们对完全实现的第五版战役的所有需求。</p><p>这款游戏捆绑了如此多的内容，以至于有些人说它代表了角色扮演游戏的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-dev-says-it-wont-elevate-the-standard-for-rpgs-because-something-cooler-will-come-along-3475653">新标准</a>”。除了增加粉丝最喜爱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-patch-9-will-add-paladins-matthew-mercer-and-better-goblin-throwing-3366809">种族和职业</a>外， <em>《博德之门 3》</em>还拥有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-reveals-murderous-shapeshifter-voiced-by-lady-dimitrescus-actor-3474795">明星云集的演员阵容</a>，他们将这些<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-director-offers-advice-on-which-character-to-play-first-3473083">角色</a>演绎得栩栩如生。</p><p>以下是您需要了解的有关<em>《博德之门 3》</em>的所有信息：</p><h2> <strong><em>《博德之门 3》</em>是什么？<br /></strong> </h2><figure id="attachment_2775770" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2775770" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-2775770 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-HERO-new@2000x1270.jpg" alt="博德之门 3" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-HERO-new@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-HERO-new@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-HERO-new@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-HERO-new@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-HERO-new@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-HERO-new@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2775770" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》。图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《博德之门 3》</em>是角色扮演游戏<em>《博德之门》</em>系列的第三部，该系列基于纸笔游戏<em>《龙与地下城》</em>中<em>被遗忘的国度</em>战役设定。该系列于 1998 年推出<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC 版</a>，随后于 2000 年推出<em>了《博德之门 2：安姆之影》</em> 。</p><p> <em>《博德之门 3》</em>基于<em>《龙与地下城》</em>规则手册第五版，但在改编为视频游戏时进行了一些修改。</p><p>至于游戏本身涉及的内容，<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1086940/Baldurs_Gate_3/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《博德之门 3》</em> Steam 页面</a>分享了以下内容：</p><p> “从<em>D&amp;D</em>玩家手册中的 12 个职业和 11 个种族中进行选择并创建自己的身份，或者扮演具有手工制作背景的 Origin 英雄。或者扮演黑暗冲动，与你内心的腐败纠缠不清，这是一个完全可定制的起源英雄，拥有自己独特的机制和故事。无论你选择成为谁，都可以在被遗忘的国度及更远的地方冒险、掠夺、战斗和浪漫。聚集你的聚会。以最多四人的队伍来进行在线冒险。”</p><h2><strong>发布日期、平台和价格</strong></h2><figure id="attachment_2772823" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2772823" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-2772823 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-3@2000x1125.jpg" alt="博德之门 3" width="2000" height="1125" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-3@2000x1125.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-3@2000x1125-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-3@2000x1125-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-3@2000x1125-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-3@2000x1125-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-3@2000x1125-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2772823" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》。图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p>在 2022 年游戏大奖颁奖典礼上，Larian Studios 透露该游戏将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-reveals-august-2023-release-date-with-new-trailer-3363338">2023 年 8 月上架</a>。</p><p>然而，在克服了看似<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-might-get-xbox-release-but-development-has-hit-issues-3404604">有问题的补丁</a>后， <em>《博德之门 3》</em>的发布日期发生了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-pc-release-date-gets-moved-forward-ps5-moved-back-3462944">变化</a>。该游戏将于 2023 年 8 月 3 日登陆 PC，但 PS5 版本将于 2023 年 9 月 6 日登陆。</p><p>预购抢先体验游戏的玩家将免费升级至<em>《博德之门 3》</em>数字豪华版。 This offers 72 hours of early access to Act One, a PC or PS5 dice skin, a digital artbook, digital character sheets, the <em>Divinity</em> Bard Song pack and more.</p><p> The Collector&#39;s Edition of the game includes everything from the Digital Deluxe Edition and a 160-page hardcover art book, tadpole keyring, cloth map of Faerûn, sticker sheet, battle diorama of Mind Flayer versus Drow Drizzt, an oversized metal D20 and lots of other goodies.</p><p> <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> is priced at <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1086940/Baldurs_Gate_3/">£49.99 for PC</a> or at <a href="https://www.playstation.com/en-gb/games/baldurs-gate-3/">£57.99 for PS5.</a> The Digital Deluxe Edition is <a href="https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10007460/">£65.99 for PS5</a> , and the Collector&#39;s Edition is <a href="https://ce.baldursgate3.game/">£259.99 for both PC and PS5</a> .</p><h2> <strong><em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> trailers</strong> </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Baldur&#039;s Gate 3 - Official Announcement Trailer" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OcP0WdH7rTs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> In 2019, Larian released the first cinematic trailer for <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> which gave players the first look at the characters, villains, and locations. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Baldur&#39;s Gate 3 - Official Early Access Trailer | 2020 年夏季游戏" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Mv2hiGHuGE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The following year, an official early access trailer was released which showcased the first in-game footage, revealing its cast of main characters, a bunch of monsters as well as being voiced by the game&#39;s own narrator. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="FULL Baldur&#039;s Gate 3 Live Gameplay Presentation" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XSc17QXxfyU?start=906&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Plenty more gameplay videos were shared by Larian when the game was in alpha as well just before Early Access launched. The footage showcased one of the first environments the player gets to experience and it was clear that many changes were made since the last time gameplay was shown off. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Baldur&#039;s Gate 3: Forging the Arcane - Official Trailer" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PNINl34JmKY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> <strong>What is the plot of <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> ?</strong> </h2><figure id="attachment_2768443" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2768443" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-2768443 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-3.jpg" alt="Baldur’s Gate 3" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2768443" class="wp-caption-text"> Baldur&#39;s Gate 3. Credit: Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> takes place almost 100 years after the events of <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 2</em> and opens with the player-made protagonist searching for a powerful cleric to heal them after being infected by a “mind flayer”.</p><p> Meanwhile, the mind flayers are the game&#39;s main antagonist. Also known as the Illithids, they have “rediscovered the secret of nautiloids” according to Vincke, and are using it to leave the Underdark and “restore their empire”.</p><p> <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> is mostly separate from the original games&#39; Bhaalspawn Saga, where children of Bhaal, the Lord Of Murder, roamed the land. “It&#39;s in living memory for some people [in the game], but most of the people who lived through it, who were very specifically attached to Baldur&#39;s Gate and the Bhaalspawn Saga, most of them are dead,” Adam Smith, a writer on <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> , told <a href="https://www.pcworld.com/article/3529768/three-hours-with-baldurs-gate-iii-no-infinity-engine-no-problem.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>PC World</em></a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3162845" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3162845" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3162845" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Baldurs-Gate-3-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="Baldur's Gate 3 patch 7 patch notes" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Baldurs-Gate-3-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Baldurs-Gate-3-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Baldurs-Gate-3-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Baldurs-Gate-3-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Baldurs-Gate-3-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Baldurs-Gate-3-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3162845" class="wp-caption-text"> Baldur&#39;s Gate 3. Credit: Larian Studios.</figcaption></figure><p> However, the RPG still includes threads from the original games. “Everything in <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 1</em> and <em>2</em> becomes more and more present as the story goes on,” Smith added. “It&#39;s not gone away. It&#39;s not forgotten and we&#39;re not doing a story which doesn&#39;t account for that.”</p><p> “You miss a lot in <em>D&amp;D</em> – if the dice are bad, you miss. That doesn&#39;t work well in a video game,” Vincke previously told <a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/baldurs-gate-3-will-combine-the-best-of-divinity-and-dandd-5th-edition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>PC Gamer</em></a> .</p><p> “If I do that, you&#39;re going to review it and say it&#39;s shit. Our approach has been implementing it as pure as we can, and then just seeing what works and what doesn&#39;t. Stuff that doesn&#39;t work, we start adapting until it does.”</p><h2> <strong>Who is the villain of <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> ?</strong> </h2><figure id="attachment_3476438" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3476438" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3476438" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/orin-the-red-maggie-robertson-baldurs-gate-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/orin-the-red-maggie-robertson-baldurs-gate-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/orin-the-red-maggie-robertson-baldurs-gate-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/orin-the-red-maggie-robertson-baldurs-gate-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/orin-the-red-maggie-robertson-baldurs-gate-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/orin-the-red-maggie-robertson-baldurs-gate-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/orin-the-red-maggie-robertson-baldurs-gate-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3476438" class="wp-caption-text"> Baldur&#39;s Gate 3. Credit: Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> As aforementioned, the Mind Flayers are the ones who have initiated an invasion of Faerûn and infected the characters with illithid parasites. However, there are three main villains that the player will encounter across their campaign.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/j-k-simmons-set-to-star-in-baldurs-gate-3-3403984">JK Simmons is playing General Ketheric Thorm</a> , a necromancer who was resurrected in order to serve as a chosen of the Absolute cult. Larian Studios expects that players will still sympathise with what Thorm has had to go through, and Simmons was a natural casting choice to embody this conflict.</p><p> “While we expected it, we were still amazed at how much his performance helped deepen the character,” said Vincke.</p><p> Lord Enver Gortash, a nefarious inventor who created scores of magical clockwork warriors, seized control of the city of Baldur&#39;s Gate following the disappearance of its previous steward. Jason Isaacs voices Gortash, saying of his character: “In a brutal world of betrayals and butchery, he&#39;s learned to lie better and backstab first.”</p><p> Lastly, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-reveals-murderous-shapeshifter-voiced-by-lady-dimitrescus-actor-3474795">Orin the Red</a> is a bloodthirsty shapeshifter obsessed with her blades, and might be the most dangerous of the three. “Orin is, affectionately, unhinged,” said Maggie Robertson, who plays the character. “你不知道她什么时候会出现，你不知道她会以什么形式出现，她非常狡猾。”</p><h2> <strong><em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> gameplay and cooperative mode<br /></strong> </h2><figure id="attachment_2772821" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2772821" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-2772821 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-1@2000x1125.jpg" alt="Baldur's Gates 3" width="2000" height="1125" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-1@2000x1125.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-1@2000x1125-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-1@2000x1125-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-1@2000x1125-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-1@2000x1125-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldur-Gates-III-1@2000x1125-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2772821" class="wp-caption-text"> Baldur&#39;s Gate 3. Credit: Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> &#39;s gameplay is generally a turn-based role-playing game, meaning you and a group of characters you can have join your party will take turns dealing damage to enemies. However, outside of battle you and your party are able to walk and around the environments freely if you turn off turn-based mode so you can carry on exploring.</p><p> You may find yourself spending a lot of time in certain areas, including the game&#39;s first location so it&#39;s especially important to explore as much as you can before moving on.</p><p> Players can choose to play the game solo and create one or more characters or play with friends in a formed party to experience the game&#39;s story together. This is Larian&#39;s first turn-based game in the <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate</em> series, similar to games like <em>Divinity: Original Sin 2</em> .</p><p> Though a party of NPCs is available to play with, players can also team up with friends via online play. The same single-player campaign is available to play with up to 4 players.</p><h2> <strong><em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> classes and races</strong> </h2><figure id="attachment_2980971" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2980971" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-2980971 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-III-2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="博德之门3" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-III-2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-III-2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-III-2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-III-2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-III-2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Baldurs-Gate-III-2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2980971" class="wp-caption-text"> Baldur&#39;s Gate 3. Credit: Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> In <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> , you&#39;re able to customize your character in some very unique ways, including allowing you to choose what race and class you would like to play for the rest of the game.</p><p> The playable races are Dragonborn, Drow, Dwarf, Elf, Githyanki, Gnome, Half-Elf, Half-Orc, Halfling, Human and Tiefling. All of these have a range of sub-races that again influence the possibilities of a playthrough.</p><p> The playable classes are <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-patch-7-adds-barbarian-class-and-improvised-weapons-3162821">Barbarian</a> , Bard, Cleric, Druid, Fighter, Monk, Paladin, Ranger, Rogue, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-patch-6-adds-sorcerer-class-and-a-fiery-new-region-3071607">Sorcerer</a> , Warlock and Wizard. These have three specialisations to choose from – for example, the Fighter can be a Battle Master, Eldritch Knight or Champion. </p><figure id="attachment_3178205" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3178205" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3178205" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Baldurs-gate-3-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="博德之门3" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Baldurs-gate-3-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Baldurs-gate-3-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Baldurs-gate-3-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Baldurs-gate-3-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Baldurs-gate-3-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Baldurs-gate-3-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3178205" class="wp-caption-text"> Baldur&#39;s Gate 3. Credit: Larian Studios.</figcaption></figure><p> Additionally, characters can also be multi-classed in <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> , according to Vincke during a <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/IAmA/comments/fhk1u3/im_swen_vincke_creative_director_at_larian/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reddit AMA session</a> . “Multiclassing rule will follow closely the [fifth edition of <em>Dungeons &amp; Dragons</em> ],” Vincke said.</p><p> “On level[ling] up, characters will be able to continue with their current class or choose a new class, provided they meet the requirements.”</p><p> Vincke also suggested that players should <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-director-offers-advice-on-which-character-to-play-first-3473083">create their own character</a> rather than step into the shoes of the seven pre-made characters. These seven origin characters are Astarion, Gale, Karlach, Lae&#39;zel, Shadowheart, The Dark Urge and Wyll.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-iii-release-date-classes-and-everything-you-need-to-know-2658339">&#39;Baldur&#39;s Gate 3&#39; release date, classes, and everything you need to know</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
